    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Keep toes toasty when adventuring, hiking or camping in the wilderness! ASR Outdoors’ Aztec and Navajo inspired mens socks are made with a polyester spandex blend, making them super soft, comfortable against your skin, more durable than cotton or wool socks and of course, will keep feet warm! With a nod to Navajo and Aztec design, these mens socks are timeless, classic and suitable to wear during all seasons. And, if you’re not packing these socks with your hiking or camping gear, they’re a comfy option for lounging at home or at the cabin or cottage; just add your favorite hot beverage or glass of whisky, a good book and cozy blanket to initiate afternoon nap sequence</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor Wilderness Adventure Performance Comfort Hiking Sock (8 Styles)</h2>\n  <p>Keep toes toasty when adventuring, hiking or camping in the wilderness! ASR Outdoors’ Aztec and Navajo inspired mens socks are made with a polyester spandex blend, making them super soft, comfortable against your skin, more durable than cotton or wool socks and of course, will keep feet warm!</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>CAMPING ACCESSORIES:</strong> Stay warm in the wilderness or on the trail with ASR Outdoors Aztec Navajo inspired mens socks; featuring a polyester spandex blend, these hiking socks are soft, comfortable, very durable and will keep feet warm</li>\n    <li><strong>AZTEC OR NAVAJO DESIGN:</strong> With a nod to Navajo and Aztec design patterns, these socks are timeless, classic and suitable for all seasons; available in blue, green, beige or brown colorways and will cover ankles and shins up to about 10 inches</li>\n    <li><strong>STOCKING STUFFERS FOR MEN:</strong> If you’re not packing these socks with your hiking or camping gear, they’re a comfy option for lounging at home or at the cabin or cottage; Great stocking stuffers for men</li>\n    <li><strong>ONE SIZE FITS MOST:</strong> ASR Outdoor mens socks feature 3% spandex for stretch and elasticity; they come one size fits most for standard US sizing</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS:</strong> Dimensions: 10 x 3.5 x 1 inches; Weight: 0.14lbs; Colors: Assorted; Care: Machine Wash Cold, Hang Dry</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1600x1600/camping_outdoors/outerwear/mens_socks_parent.jpg\" alt=\"Keep toes toasty when adventuring, hiking or camping in the wilderness\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>Size:</strong> One Size: Regular</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>With a nod to Navajo and Aztec design, these mens socks are timeless, classic and suitable to wear during all seasons. And, if you’re not packing these socks with your hiking or camping gear, they’re a comfy option for lounging at home or at the cabin or cottage; just add your favorite hot beverage or glass of whisky, a good book and cozy blanket to initiate afternoon nap sequence. These hiking socks feature 3% spandex for stretch and elasticity and will cover ankles and shins up to about ten inches; one size fits most.</p>\n  <p>A